OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,FITV News Political Editor Robert
OL,7,FPeston gives his analysis of Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer's latest remarks during his
OL,9,Fdiplomatic tour of the Gulf states
OL,11,FThe prime minister said on Friday that
OL,12,Fit is "in America's interest" to be
OL,13,Fpart of Nato after Donald Trump
OL,14,Fcontinued his threats to pull out of
OL,15,Fthe alliance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
