PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of his departure from
OL,7,Fthe Middle East after a two-day visit,
OL,8,FSir Keir Starmer said European
OL,9,Fcountries, including the UK, need to
OL,10,Fbe doing more to keep the alliance
OL,11,Fstrong.
OL,13,FHe said: "We're very strong supporters
OL,14,Fof Nato and I've been making the
OL,15,Fargument for some considerable time
OL,16,Fthat we need to do more.
OL,18,F"It's the single most effective
OL,19,Fmilitary alliance the world has ever
OL,20,Fknown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,F"Do we Europeans need to do more? Yes,
OL,7,FI've been making that argument for the
OL,8,Fbest part of two years, to our
OL,9,FEuropean partners as much as anybody
OL,10,Felse.
OL,12,F"We continue to make that case and we
OL,13,Fwill make that case."
OL,15,FStarmer speaks ahead of his departure
OL,16,Ffrom Qatar
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
