CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,FHe added: "It is in America's
OL,7,Finterests, it's in European interests.
OL,8,FNato is a defensive alliance, which
OL,9,Ffor decades has kept us much safer
OL,10,Fthan we would otherwise have been."
OL,12,FThe PM's comment come after a call
OL,13,Fwith the US president on Thursday
OL,14,Fnight, where the pair discussed the
OL,15,Fneed for a "practical plan" to get
OL,16,Fshipping going through the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
