OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,FSpeaking about the conversation, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "I had a discussion with
OL,8,FPresident Trump last night and set out
OL,9,Fto him the views of the region here,
OL,10,Fthese Gulf states are the neighbours
OL,11,Fof Iran, and therefore, if the
OL,12,Fceasefire is to hold ` and we hope it
OL,13,Fwill - it has to involve them.
OL,15,F"They have very strong views on the
OL,16,FStrait of Hormuz. We spent most of the
OL,17,Ftime on the call talking about the
OL,18,Fpractical plan that's going to be
OL,19,Fneeded to get navigation through the
OL,20,Fstrait and the role that the UK is
OL,21,Fplaying."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
