OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,FOn Thursday, the prime minister told
OL,7,FITV News' Talking Politics in an
OL,8,Fexclusive interview that he is "fed
OL,9,Fup" with families in the UK seeing
OL,10,Ftheir bills go up and down "because of
OL,11,Fthe actions of Putin or Trump", after
OL,12,Fthe closure of the strait caused stock
OL,13,Fmarkets to plummet worldwide and oil
OL,14,Fprices to sharply increase.
OL,16,FThe UK has been working to bring
OL,17,Ftogether a coalition of countries to
OL,18,Fcome up with a plan to get shipping
OL,19,Fmoving through the route again, after
OL,20,FIran's effective closure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,FThat included political and diplomatic
OL,7,Fefforts, but also "looking at military
OL,8,Fcapabilities" and the logistics of
OL,9,Factually moving vessels through the
OL,10,Fstrait.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, the US and Iran agreed
OL,13,Fto a two-week ceasefire, with further
OL,14,Ftalks to start in Islamabad, Pakistan,
OL,15,Fover the weekend.
OL,17,FAs he left the Middle East, Starmer
OL,18,Facknowledged the ceasefire is
OL,19,F"fragile", and that "more work is
OL,20,Fneeded" from the UK to help allies in
OL,21,Fthe Gulf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
