OL,3,CStarmer says Nato is 'in America's
OL,4,Cinterest' after call with Trump
OL,6,FHe added: "This conflict is going to
OL,7,Fdefine us for a generation and we must
OL,8,Frespond, and we will respond, with
OL,9,Fstrength."
